Feature adaptation of Beatrix Potter's classic tale of a rebellious rabbit trying to sneak into a farmer's vegetable garden.

Peter Rabbit and family take over the manor house of Old McGregor when he dies, but McGregor’s nephew arrives to claim his inheritance (on leave from his job at Harrod’s), so bunnies wreak havoc to win it back. McGregor begins dating neighbor Bea (loyal friend of bunnies) to learn bunny vulnerabilities, but a raging war ends up destroying Bea’s cottage instead. The factions make amends while winning Bea back, and wage peace in the end.

[00:00:30:00-00:02:00:23] Peter Rabbit races through the countryside. [00:02:01:00-00:03:35:13] Peter Rabbit heads to Old McGregor's garden to get something to eat. [00:03:35:14-00:05:37:07] Peter Rabbit and his family take food from Old McGregor's garden. [00:05:37:08-00:07:36:16] Old McGregor looks for Peter Rabbit in the garden. [00:07:36:17-00:08:09:10] Bea tells the rabbits that the garden belongs to Old McGregor. [00:08:09:11-00:08:54:08] Bea invites the rabbits inside when it's raining. [00:08:54:09-00:10:38:01] Peter Rabbit remembers what happened to his father. [00:10:38:02-00:12:21:20] Peter Rabbit goes back into the garden to retrieve his jacket. [00:12:21:21-00:12:59:14] Peter Rabbit tells his family that Old McGregor is gone. [00:12:59:15-00:15:02:15] All the animals take over Old McGregor's garden. [00:15:02:16-00:15:39:13] Peter Rabbit and the other animals party in Old McGregor's house. [00:15:39:14-00:16:37:19] Mr. McGregor trains his staff to pay attention to every detail in the store. [00:16:37:20-00:18:41:12] Mr. McGregor doesn't get the promotion he wanted. [00:18:41:13-00:19:12:06] Mr. McGregor's boss advises him to get some perspective. [00:19:12:07-00:20:27:01] Peter Rabbit and his sisters hang up a portrait of their parents. [00:20:27:02-00:21:24:21] Mr. McGregor finds out that he's inherited a farm. [00:21:24:22-00:21:56:09] Mr. McGregor travels to Windermere. [00:21:56:10-00:24:01:02] The animals hide as Mr. McGregor approaches the house. [00:24:01:03-00:25:06:04] Mr. McGregor chases the animals out of his house. [00:25:06:05-00:27:05:01] Mr. McGregor begins cleaning the house and garden. [00:27:05:02-00:29:17:16] Mr. McGregor closes off the garden. [00:29:17:17-00:31:18:07] Bea gives Mr. McGregor some binoculars for birdwatching. [00:31:18:08-00:32:32:00] Peter Rabbit and Benjamin Bunny sneak into the garden. [00:32:32:01-00:34:21:21] Peter Rabbit and Benjamin Bunny hide from Mr. McGregor. [00:34:21:22-00:36:46:19] Peter Rabbit, Flopsy, Mopsy, and Cotton-tail try to save Benjamin Bunny from Mr. McGregor. [00:36:46:20-00:38:18:16] Mr. McGregor drives into town, not knowing the rabbits are in the back of his truck. [00:38:18:17-00:40:42:21] Mr. McGregor buys some explosives to get rid of the rabbits. [00:40:42:22-00:42:01:18] Mr. McGregor gives Bea a ride home. [00:42:01:19-00:44:05:13] Bea invites Mr. McGregor over for a drink. [00:44:05:14-00:46:23:23] Mr. McGregor and Bea grow closer together and share a picnic. [00:46:24:00-00:47:04:19] Bea wins the game. [00:47:04:20-00:49:24:13] Peter Rabbit and Mr. McGregor fight in Bea's art studio. [00:49:24:14-00:50:20:14] Bea scolds Peter Rabbit for ruining her painting. [00:50:20:15-00:50:35:17] JW Rooster II realizes the consequences of his actions. [00:50:35:18-00:51:39:20] Peter Rabbit prepares his troops for battle. [00:51:39:21-00:53:03:14] Mr. McGregor wakes up to an unpleasant surprise. [00:53:03:15-00:54:30:20] Mrs. Tiggy-Winkle touches the electric fence. [00:54:30:21-00:56:49:02] The rabbits use Mr. McGregor's electric fence against him. [00:56:49:03-00:58:05:03] Mr. McGregor puts explosives in the rabbit hole. [00:58:05:04-00:59:25:21] Benjamin Bunny has second thoughts about supporting Peter Rabbit's plan. [00:59:25:22-01:01:34:11] The rabbits shoot blackberries at Mr. McGregor. [01:01:34:12-01:03:39:18] Mopsy tells Flopsy a secret while the others fight Mr. McGregor. [01:03:39:19-01:05:59:00] Mr. McGregor catches Peter Rabbit. [01:05:59:01-01:07:30:14] Mr. McGregor tells Bea that Peter Rabbit pushed the detonator. [01:07:30:15-01:07:43:03] JW Rooster II and his chicks greet a new day. [01:07:43:04-01:09:54:02] Peter Rabbit regrets what he did to Bea. [01:09:54:03-01:10:58:15] Mr. McGregor's boss offers him a job. [01:10:58:16-01:12:24:06] Peter Rabbit apologizes to Benjamin Bunny, Flopsy, Mopsy, and Cotton-tail. [01:12:24:07-01:13:23:01] Flopsy, Mopsy, and Cotton-tail argue over who is the oldest.
